s:4:"desc";s:38:"Enter your Youtube URL if you have one";s:2:"id";s:13:"elite_youtube";s:3:"std";s:0:"";s:4:"type";s:4:"text";}i:45;a:2:{s:4:"name";s:15:"Styling Options";s:4:"type";s:7:"heading";}i:46;a:6:{s:4:"name";s:16:"Theme Stylesheet";s:4:"desc";s:44:"Select your themes alternative color scheme.";s:2:"id";s:19:"elite_altstylesheet";s:3:"std";s:5:"black";s:4:"type";s:6:"select";s:7:"options";a:10:{s:7:"default";s:7:"default";s:5:"black";s:5:"black";s:5:"brown";s:5:"brown";s:4:"blue";s:4:"blue";s:6:"orange";s:6:"orange";s:4:"pink";s:4:"pink";s:6:"purple";s:6:"purple";s:3:"red";s:3:"red";s:5:"green";s:5:"green";s:5:"olive";s:5:"olive";}}i:47;a:5:{s:4:"name";s:10:"Custom CSS";s:4:"desc";s:62:"Quickly add some CSS to your theme by adding it to this block.";s:2:"id";s:15:"elite_customcss";s:3:"std";s:0:"";s:4:"type";s:8:"textarea";}i:48;a:2:{s:4:"name";s:15:"Footer Settings";s:4:"type";s:7:"heading";}i:49;a:5:{s:4:"name";s:11:"Footer Text";s:4:"desc";s:45:"Enter text you want to be displayed on Footer";s:2:"id";s:16:"elite_footertext";s:3:"std";s:0:"";s:4:"type";s:4:"text";}i:50;a:2:{s:4:"name";s:11:"SEO Options";s:4:"type";s:7:"heading";}i:51;a:5:{s:4:"name";s:31:"Meta Keywords (comma separated)";s:4:"desc";s:164:"Meta keywords provide search engines with additional information about topics that appear on your site. This only applies to your home page. Keyword Limit Maximum 8";s:2:"id";s:13:"elite_keyword";s:3:"std";s:0:"";s:4:"type";s:8:"textarea";}i:52;a:5:{s:4:"name";s:16:"Meta Description";s:4:"desc";s:219:"You should use meta descriptions to provide search engines with additional information about topics that appear on your site. This only applies to your home page.Optimal Length for Search Engines, Roughly 155 Characters";s:2:"id";s:17:"elite_description";s:3:"std";s:0:"";s:4:"type";s:8:"textarea";}i:53;a:5:{s:4:"name";s:16:"Meta Author Name";s:4:"desc";s:87:"You should write the full name of the author here. This only applies to your home page.";s:2:"id";s:12:"elite_author";s:3:"std";s:0:"";s:4:"type";s:8:"textarea";}}s:12:"of_themename";s:16:"Responsive Theme";s:12:"of_shortname";s:2:"of";s:13:"elite_favicon";s:0:"";s:12:"elite_bodybg";s:0:"";s:15:"elite_analytics";s:0:"";s:5:"re_nm";s:2:"on";s:17:"elite_slideimage1";s:64:"http://localhost/yolonepal/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/image2.jpg";s:17:"elite_sliderhead1";s:14:"Colorful Tiger";s:17:"elite_sliderdesc1";s:280:"They are funding Go, Clang, the Closure compiler, etc. I''m not Google''s biggest fan, but they are contributing quite a bit. Go''s elegant, well-thought-out concurrency model was a major inspiration behind Clojure''s core.async, which was critical to getting Clojure in the browser. ";s:21:"elite_slidelink_text1";s:0:"";s:16:"elite_slidelink1";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_slideimage2";s:104:"http://localhost/yolonepal/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/no-excuses-nike-football_1024x768_338-standard.jpg";s:17:"elite_sliderhead2";s:17:"No Excuses Please";s:17:"elite_sliderdesc2";s:364:"If you''re a startup, the advantage of Clojure over Java is a game-changer. Google, on the other hand, doesn''t need to get software out fast. When you''re not interested in rapid prototyping, Java and C++ are "good enough". If you care about beauty in tools (i.e. it has to be Lisp) rather than effectiveness only then Google is probably not the right place for you.";s:21:"elite_slidelink_text2";s:0:"";s:16:"elite_slidelink2";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_slideimage3";s:78:"http://localhost/yolonepal/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/street_art_74_banksy.jpg";s:17:"elite_sliderhead3";s:20:"Street Art with Kids";s:17:"elite_sliderdesc3";s:392:"Did Scala come from a large company like Google? No. Clojure? No. Big companies tend either not to care about languages that much (just make it work) or to become hellbent on language unification (or, at least, a tight whitelist) to a degree that isn''t healthy. Google is a solidly above-average tech company but I don''t think we should expect it to innovate in languages; that''s not its job.";s:21:"elite_slidelink_text3";s:0:"";s:16:"elite_slidelink3";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_slideimage4";s:73:"http://localhost/yolonepal/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Wallpaper-l-027.jpg";s:17:"elite_sliderhead4";s:10:"Is it War?";s:17:"elite_sliderdesc4";s:281:"Google created both Google Web Toolkit and the Dart language as alternatives to writing in Javascript. Then they have AngularJS and componentJS and Polymer for creating applications in Javascript. They also created the V8 engine and Closure compiler to make  Javascript run faster.";s:21:"elite_slidelink_text4";s:0:"";s:16:"elite_slidelink4";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_slideimage5";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_sliderhead5";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_sliderdesc5";s:0:"";s:21:"elite_slidelink_text5";s:0:"";s:16:"elite_slidelink5";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_slideimage6";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_sliderhead6";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_sliderdesc6";s:0:"";s:21:"elite_slidelink_text6";s:0:"";s:16:"elite_slidelink6";s:0:"";s:14:"elite_homehead";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_homecontent";s:0:"";s:15:"elite_portfolio";s:13:"Uncategorized";s:14:"elite_facebook";s:0:"";s:13:"elite_twitter";s:0:"";s:9:"elite_rss";s:0:"";s:12:"elite_google";s:0:"";s:12:"elite_flickr";s:0:"";s:14:"elite_pintrust";s:0:"";s:13:"elite_youtube";s:0:"";s:19:"elite_altstylesheet";s:4:"blue";s:15:"elite_customcss";s:0:"";s:16:"elite_footertext";s:36:"Yolo Nepal 2013. All rights reserved";s:13:"elite_keyword";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_description";s:0:"";s:12:"elite_author";s:0:"";s:10:"of_options";a:51:{s:10:"elite_logo";s:0:"";s:13:"elite_favicon";s:0:"";s:12:"elite_bodybg";s:0:"";s:15:"elite_analytics";s:0:"";s:5:"re_nm";s:2:"on";s:17:"elite_slideimage1";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_sliderhead1";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_sliderdesc1";s:0:"";s:21:"elite_slidelink_text1";s:0:"";s:16:"elite_slidelink1";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_slideimage2";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_sliderhead2";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_sliderdesc2";s:0:"";s:21:"elite_slidelink_text2";s:0:"";s:16:"elite_slidelink2";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_slideimage3";s:0:"";s:17:"elite_sliderhead3"