"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/AdrotatePluginForWordpress/~3/G43wcd0qcjo/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:83:"http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2013/12/adrotate-pro-3-8-16-important-fixes/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Sat, 07 Dec 2013 12:54:56 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"Updates";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"blocks";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"bugfix";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"features";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3:"pro";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:37:"http://www.adrotateplugin.com/?p=9004";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:577:"<p>A small update but with some important fixes. You&#8217;re advised to upgrade as soon as you&#8217;re able. This version fixes an issue with blocks where the margins were applied double. This bug was introduced in version 3.8.14. On top of that, if you let your advertisers create and upload their own ads, filenames were not [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href="http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2013/12/adrotate-pro-3-8-16-important-fixes/">AdRotate Pro 3.8.16 &#8211; Important fixes!</a> appeared first on <a href="http://www.adrotateplugin.com">AdRotate for WordPress</a>.</p>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Arnan de Gans";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1808:"<p>A small update but with some important fixes. You&#8217;re advised to upgrade as soon as you&#8217;re able.</p>\n<p>This version fixes an issue with blocks where the margins were applied double. This bug was introduced in version 3.8.14.<br />\nOn top of that, if you let your advertisers create and upload their own ads, filenames were not properly sanitised.If people use a faulty filename it may cause errors and crashes.<br />\nAnd lastly, if multiple advertisers create adverts they may run into an issue where that is not possible giving an error about invalid AD Id&#8217;s.</p>\n<p>And a more fun addition (This will also be in the Free version in the next update). If your sidebar has a big padding around the widgets. AdRotate can now override that space, allowing you to place bigger ads in your sidebar.</p>\n<h3>Changes</h3>\n<div class="shortcode-unorderedlist arrow"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>[fix] Invalid ad ID when multiple advertisers create ads simultaneously</li>\n<li>[fix] Better sanitize filenames for advertiser ads</li>\n<li>[fix] Dynamic and Block div size</li>\n<li>[new] Remove padding from Widgets to clear more space for ads</li>\n</ul>\n<p></div>\n\n<h3>Did you know?</h3>\n<p>If you&#8217;re unsure how to upgrade or simply do not have the time &#8211; I can do it for you: <a href="http://www.adrotateplugin.com/shop/installation-and-upgrades/upgrade/" title="Upgrade AdRotate">http://www.adrotateplugin.com/shop/installation-and-upgrades/upgrade/</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href="http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2013/12/adrotate-pro-3-8-16-important-fixes/">AdRotate Pro 3.8.16 &#8211; Important fixes!</a> appeared first on <a href="http://www.adrotateplugin.com">AdRotate for WordPress</a>.</p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/AdrotatePluginForWordpress/~4/G43wcd0qcjo" height="1" width="1"/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:79:"http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2013/12/adrotate-pro-3-8-16-important-fixes/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:74:"http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2013/12/adrotate-pro-3-8-16-important-fixes/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:54:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:35:"New Orleans Local uses AdRotate Pro";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:73:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/AdrotatePluginForWordpress/~3/gwG1zUbIpjA/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:83:"http://www.adrotateplugin.com/2013/12/new-orleans-local-uses-adrotate-pro/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a: